        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tab-pane fade" id="nav-usetype" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-features-tab">
        <hr>
        <strong>Use Type</strong>
        <hr>
        <% if @car.allow_personal_commercial_use%>
          <p>This vehicle may be used on unsealed roads as indicated by the car owner</p>
        <%else%>
          <p>This vehicle as indicated by the car owner may only be used on sealed roads.</p>
        <% end%>
      </div>
      <div class="tab-pane fade" id="nav-allwance" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-allwance-tab">
        <hr>
        <strong>Daily Drive Allowance</strong>
        <hr>
        <p>150 kilometers is the daily distance driven odometer allowance on this car. <br>
        Odometer allowance starts at pick up & ends at the time of drop off.<br>
        As a courtesy please notify car owner in advance if you plan on using the vehicle 50 km over the set allowance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
